All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file,
UIX improvement and code management is not included in this file.

[3.9.4]
- coming soon...

[3.9.3]
- new workplane, draw anywhere in the space with a transformable workplane!
- new sphere generator
- fix color palette (canvas height > 64000px is not supported by chrome)
- update and speed up fill tool
- update bakery to respect voxel colors (bind to vertex colors)

[3.9.2]
- new optional uvs for bakery
- new axis-view similar to blender
- ghostvoxels updated to colored thin-instances
- calc azimuthal angle of the axis-view for drone camera
- improve renderer and fix ACES tone mapping
- unify perspective and orthographic zoom
- make onion-skin persistent
- speed up dynamic palette generation with a canvas layer (no more ul/li tags)
- update scene grid, faster and more accurate

[3.9.1]
- new load from MagicaVoxel .vox file
- new box-bake
- new custom confirm dialog (window.confirm deprecated)
- new renderer show voxels if there is no bake to render
- change file extension to ".vbx" to prevent conflict
- speed up box tools preview (from 5 fps to 60 fps)
- remove marquee tool (save 200 lines)
- speed up voxel data load time
- split storage for voxels and bakes
- speed up voxelization (2x faster)
- update scene to right-handed system
- improve rendering and fix SSAO

[3.9.0]
- new pull-color tool
- new fixed height for box-add (draw walls)
- new symmetry support for box-add, box-remove and box-paint tools
- fix color bucket performance issue
- fix touch not drawing rapidly
- fix unwanted undo records on camera movement
- speed up SPS by eliminating the need for computeParticleColor
- improve bake to mesh, gamma correct bakery colors
- improve rendering for all 3 modes

[3.8.9]
- new box-add, box-remove and box-paint tools
- new reduce voxels (10x10x10 - 512 deleted = 488 voxels)
- update file format to a new expandable ini (smaller file size)
- loader detect old format, your data is safe and automagically updated

[3.8.8]
- new fill tool with ray caster
- new quick save and load bakes
- new pixel-monk joined the party!
- fix and improve undo/redo

[3.8.7]
- new post-process settings
- new import baked meshes from VOX file
- fix z-fighting (double-sided planes issue)
- fix debug layer crash and fix exported glb for blender (material string-float issue)
- fix bakery materials, polish merge tool, respect instances
- update bakery to single-sided, 50% less vertices, faster and smaller file size

[3.8.6]
- new interactive merge tool, merge bakes
- new screenshot with pixel density enhancement
- fix terrain, missing voxels on higher heights
- update material and texture workflow

[3.8.5]
- new photographic reticle and joystick controls for touchscreen (render mode)
- new bake all and split by color groups

[3.8.4]
- new baked mesh is clean, no shared faces, grouped by color
- new electron package for desktop users
- new save file dialog for chrome browser
- major bug fixes and code improvements

[3.8.3]
- improve render pipeline
- improve camera, add multiple cameras

[3.8.2]
- new separated modeling and bakery modes
- improve bakery, baked meshes attached to project and stored in vox file
- improve hdri and rendering quality

[3.8.1]
- new integrated asset-viewer (preview/convert/copy model)
- improve pbr material for baked meshes and exported glb

[3.8.0]
- new marquee selection tool
- new orthographic camera
- improve pbr material with environment and textures
- user-defined texture slots
- simplify color layers to just colors!

[3.7.8]
- new project name for file io
- new hdri environment for pbr material
- new isometric generator

[3.7.4]
- update engine to Babylon 5.0.0+
- new image voxelization
- bug 5.x -> workplane/grid -> scaling animation issue
- bug 5.x -> tool -> transform -> setOverlayCube -> normal scaling issue
- bug 5.x -> tool -> remove -> ghostVoxel -> another scaling (overlap) issue!
- bug camera -> framing behavior -> unable to draw at bottom view
